raw_text = "# SPDX-FileCopyrightText: The Threadbare Authors
# SPDX-License-Identifier: MPL-2.0
~ start
Bill spots a creepy looking castle in the distance. He knows he probably has to go there for his mission to continue.
But a lake filled with slippery stones are in his way. Bill must traverse the stones to proceed to the castle. 
Bill: GULP!
=> END
~ well_done
Bill: I made it!  
Bill has found a thread, which means the castle is his last stop.
Determined now, he heads towards the Castle.
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
